TROUBLESHOOTING:
===============
If you encounter "Package parsing error":
1. Ensure Android version is 5.0 or higher
2. Re-download the APK file (may be corrupted)
3. Clear browser cache and download again
4. Try installing through different file manager
5. Ensure sufficient storage space (50MB+)

If app crashes on startup:
1. Clear app data: Settings > Apps > LoanBondhu > Clear Data
2. Restart device and try again
3. Reinstall the application
4. Check if internet connection is available

Admin login issues:
1. Use exact phone number: 01650074073
2. Password is case-sensitive: admin123
3. 2FA code: 123456
4. Clear app cache if login fails repeatedly

